---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
	title="About | Engineering & Code"
	description="About me - Computer Engineering Student."
>
	<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-8">About Me</h1>

		<div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
			<p>
				I'm a Computer Engineering student passionate about transforming
				complex problems into simple and efficient solutions. My journey
				began with curiosity about how things work "under the hood",
				which led me to explore everything from hardware to modern web
				development.
			</p>

			<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">My Approach</h3>
			<p>
				I believe technology should serve the business purpose, not the
				other way around. Combining my background in WordPress and SEO
				with modern technologies like Astro and React, I create
				applications that not only work but perform and convert.
			</p>

			<h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">Tech Stack</h3>
			<ul class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 list-none pl-0">
				<li class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<span class="text-emerald-400">✓</span> JavaScript/TypeScript
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<span class="text-emerald-400">✓</span> React & Next.js
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<span class="text-emerald-400">✓</span> Astro & SSG
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<span class="text-emerald-400">✓</span> Python & Automation
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<span class="text-emerald-400">✓</span> WordPress & PHP
				</li>
				<li class="flex items-center gap-2">
					<span class="text-emerald-400">✓</span> SQL & NoSQL
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>

		<div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-slate-800 flex justify-center">
			<a
				href={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/projects/seo-optimization`}
				class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors"
			>
				<svg
					xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
					width="20"
					height="20"
					viewBox="0 0 24 24"
					fill="none"
					stroke="currentColor"
					stroke-width="2"
					stroke-linecap="round"
					stroke-linejoin="round"
					><path d="M21 15v4a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-4"
					></path><polyline points="7 10 12 15 17 10"></polyline><line
						x1="12"
						x2="12"
						y1="15"
						y2="3"></line></svg
				>
				Download CV
			</a>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>
